OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772201047
OL,3,CMan who raped woman while holding her
OL,4,Ccaptive is given 14-year prison
OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FA man who repeatedly raped a woman,
OL,8,Fheld a gun to her head and falsely
OL,9,Fimprisoned her during a weekend-long
OL,10,Fordeal has been given a 14-year prison
OL,11,Fsentence.
OL,13,FCarlisle Crown Court heard on Friday
OL,14,F27 February of the emotional turmoil
OL,15,Fthat Noah Hetherington's crimes had on
OL,16,Fhis victim, who described going
OL,17,Fthrough "pure hell" as she was held
OL,18,Fcaptive at an address over several
OL,19,Fdays.
OL,26,@yD@IOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
