OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772201047
OL,3,CMan who raped woman while holding her
OL,4,Ccaptive is given 14-year prison
OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FHetherington, aged 22, initially held
OL,8,Fwhat appeared to be a real shotgun to
OL,9,Fthe woman's head and threatened to
OL,10,Fshoot her if she left him. He raped
OL,11,Fher several times, struck her legs
OL,12,Fwith an axe handle, causing bruising
OL,13,Fand also removed her phone SIM card to
OL,14,Fprevent ready access.
OL,16,FHetherington was said to have also
OL,17,Fsmoked cannabis, taken cocaine and
OL,18,Fdrank alcohol during a period of
OL,19,F"complete control" over the woman.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772201047
OL,3,CMan who raped woman while holding her
OL,4,Ccaptive is given 14-year prison
OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FFather-of-two Hetherington ` a roofer
OL,8,Fand joiner ` denied multiple rape
OL,9,Fcharges, false imprisonment, actual
OL,10,Fbodily harm assault and possessing an
OL,11,Fimitation firearm with intent to cause
OL,12,Ffear of violence. But he was convicted
OL,13,Fof these offences by jurors following
OL,14,Fa trial.
OL,16,FIn an impact statement, the woman
OL,17,Fsaid: "I feel like, unfortunately, on
OL,18,Fthat weekend when he did that to me I
OL,19,Fwas almost dead and killed; dead and
OL,20,Fburied. Because I've never been the
OL,21,Fsame person since."
OL,26,@yD@GOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772201047
OL,3,CMan who raped woman while holding her
OL,4,Ccaptive is given 14-year prison
OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FThe woman spoke of being in and out of
OL,8,Fhospital after her ordeal, feeling
OL,9,Fstressed, losing hair and also being
OL,10,Funable to eat and sleep.
OL,12,FOn giving evidence at Hetherington's
OL,13,Ftrial, she described doing that "for
OL,14,Fthe future".
OL,26,@uD@aOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772201047
OL,3,CMan who raped woman while holding her
OL,4,Ccaptive is given 14-year prison
OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,F"Because he's a dangerous man and I
OL,8,Fbelieve he will kill somebody. So I'm
OL,9,Fdoing this to more prevent him from
OL,10,Fdoing it again, not for me," she
OL,11,Fexplained. "He needs to be stopped.
OL,12,FAnd that's the only reason I'm trying
OL,13,Fto be strong and get through it ` for
OL,14,Fother people; for other girls."
OL,16,FThe woman added: "I've been
OL,17,Ftraumatised and I'll live with the
OL,18,Ftrauma every single day."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@\O]sD@LOUvD@_O]xD@ROUzD@YO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772201047
OL,3,CMan who raped woman while holding her
OL,4,Ccaptive is given 14-year prison
OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FHer father, in a statement, described
OL,8,Fthe marked changes in relationship
OL,9,Fbetween the pair since her ordeal at
OL,10,FHetherington's hands. "Ever since, our
OL,11,Ffamily life has changed completely,"
OL,12,Fhe stated.
OL,14,FThe court heard Hetherington,
OL,15,Fpreviously of Maryport Road, Dearham,
OL,16,Fhad previous convictions for offensive
OL,17,Fweapon possession ` after taking a
OL,18,Fsharpened stick into school ` along
OL,19,Fwith battery, damage, drug and driving
OL,20,Fcrimes.
OL,26,@rD@WOUsD@dO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772201047
OL,3,CMan who raped woman while holding her
OL,4,Ccaptive is given 14-year prison
OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FHe was said to have made positive
OL,8,Fprogress while remanded in custody,
OL,9,Fproviding negative drug and alcohol
OL,10,Ftests. A defence barrister spoke of
OL,11,Fhis immaturity and said there had
OL,12,Flatterly been concern about his mental
OL,13,Fhealth.
OL,15,FImposing the lengthy jail term, Judge
OL,16,FNicholas Barker told Hetherington: "It
OL,17,Fis clear to me that, despite your age,
OL,18,Fyou have entrenched criminal
OL,19,Ftendencies, which you have not
OL,20,Faddressed when you have had the
OL,21,Fopportunity to do so."
OL,26,@xD@dOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
