OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772201047
OL,3,CMan who raped woman while holding her
OL,4,Ccaptive is given 14-year prison
OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FHetherington will serve two-thirds of
OL,8,Fthe jail term before being considered
OL,9,Ffor release. He must sign the sex
OL,10,Foffender register, indefinitely, and
OL,11,Fcomply with the conditions of a sexual
OL,12,Fharm prevention order.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/8
